item.title: CVE-2020-6654|2024-08-04T09:11:04.905Z -- eaton -- 9000x%20programming%20and%20configuration%20software
item.description: A DLL Hijacking vulnerability in Eaton's 9000x Programming and Configuration Software v 2.0.38 and prior allows an attacker to execute arbitrary code by replacing the required DLLs with malicious DLLs when the software try to load vci11un6.DLL and cinpl.DLL.
